# Tunisian Market Context

## Language Mix (CRITICAL)

| Context | Language | Script |
|---------|----------|--------|
| Headlines, CTAs, slogans | Tunisian Darija | Arabic script |
| Body text, descriptions | French | Latin script |
| Technical/admin | French or English | Latin script |

**Examples of Darija CTAs:**
- "علاش جاي؟" (Why are you here? — Goal navigator)
- "واش مازلت محيّر؟" (Still undecided? — Final CTA)
- "شري دوك" / "Chri Tawa" (Buy now)
- Arabic font: **Cairo** (Google Fonts)

## Currency

- **TND** (Tunisian Dinar) — ALWAYS after the amount
- Format: `89.00 TND` or `129.990 TND`
- Never use "DT", "Dinar", or "$"

## Geography

- 24 Governorates (gouvernorats): `lib/constants/gouvernorats.ts`
- Greater Tunis: Tunis, Ariana, Ben Arous, Manouba
- Shipping: Ciblex (national), local delivery (Tunis area)

## Payment

- **COD only** (Cash on Delivery) — standard in Tunisia
- No online payment yet (Flouci/Konnect planned for future)

## User Communication

- Project manager (Dali) communicates in **Tunisian Darija**
- Mix of Arabic + French words in same sentences
- Respond in English or French (not Darija)
- Understand Darija input, respond formally

## Business Hours / Context

